In [[Digital Performer]] you can create custom click patterns.

[[File:Digital Performer pattern clicks.png|right|thumb|Pattern clicks window]]

==Custom click pattern==

#Go to '''Digital performer / preferences'''
#Go to '''Click defaults'''
#Click '''Add''' to create a new click pattern and then scroll to the bottom of the list to see the click pattern you just created (it will be a "generic" default click).
#Click the '''Beat Value''' menu and change it to pattern. You can add a custom numerical pattern. To accent a click in the pattern, highlight it and use the key command '''Command+B'''.
#Save the custom pattern by selecting '''Save Pattern''' in the pattern drop down menu.





